INSERT INTO orders (hash, offerer, zone, zone_hash, start_time, end_time,
        order_type, total_original_consideration_items, counter, salt, conduit_key, signature)
        VALUES ($1, $2::TEXT::citext, $3::TEXT::citext, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, $10, $11, $12) ON CONFLICT (hash) DO NOTHING

180037a9710afd6b9d325c5ffadccb76a077a118.query: UPDATE orders SET cancelled = true WHERE offerer = $1::TEXT::citext AND counter < $2
